## Field reference

`**service_name**`
: URL-safe slug. Must match the folder under `{{workspace_dir}}/helm/`
  and `{{workspace_dir}}/docker/`. The harness resolves
  `release_name` from this via `conventions.release_name`.

`**technology**`
: The upstream project and (when relevant) version. Used by the
  runtime-diagnoser to pick the right upstream docs.

`**dependency**`
: Other sub-goals that must be deployed first. `[none]` if
  standalone. Agents scaffold in dependency order.

`**artifacts**`
: One or both of `helm`, `docker`. Decides which author skill to
  load and which CLI stages run. **Required** — phase-spec-reader
  warns when missing.
